{"tid":384224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【奇景】機場附近有12個水龍捲 客機安然越過降落","createTime":"2017-09-02T06:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T06:56:21.000Z","uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f26c2e14a2c27430ad9279f948e547b5b593393","tid":384224,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯黑海沿岸日前天氣惡劣，一架客機在索契降落時遇到3個水龍捲，場面驚險。所幸客機最後在3個水龍捲之間穿過，順利安全降落。<br />\n<br />\n事發在周二，當時天色昏暗，烏雲密布，海上出現至少3個水龍捲，其間一架客機飛至，逐一穿過水龍捲，似乎不受影響，最後安全降落。大批民眾在岸邊目睹這驚險一幕。<br />\n<br />\n據報當時附近出現多達12個水龍捲，由於天氣惡劣，至少9班航班要轉飛其他機場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g4nof3s9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg4nof3s9&h=28a26ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a7b8ec23c6c8a0e2d32550ed2bf203abc3471a","tid":384224,"uid":67248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:42:40.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c09b90f63744fded69701b711fd7459d56dd70e","tid":384224,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cade83fd1bbc4d5889abb9b8716a9aa553a1904","tid":384224,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"睇片唔係穿過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}